title: Kendall Jenner cuts pretty figure in bright yellow outfit for lunch date with Kourtney Kardashian and Kris Jenner
text:
Kendall Jenner cuts pretty figure in bright yellow outfit for lunch date with Kourtney Kardashian and Kris Jenner The 21-year-old looked chic in a pair of wide leg trousers and a slinky top Share Ray of sunshine: Kendall Jenner (Photo: X17Online) Share Get daily updates directly to your inbox + Subscribe Could not subscribe, try again later Invalid Email 
Kendall Jenner was a ray of sunshine when she stepped out for lunch on Wednesday. 
The 21-year-old model met up with mum Kris Jenner and sister Kourtney to film scenes for Keeping Up With The Kardashians in Calabasas, California. 
The star, whose mood didn't appear to match her outfit, ditched her signature skinny jeans and laid back tees for a slinky yellow top that featured lace around the neckline. 
She teamed the top with baggy yellow trousers and finished off the look with huge hoop earrings, a matching yellow clutch bag and a fuss-free slick back hairstyle. Kendall Jenner (Photo: AZ-ROL/X17online.com) Kendall Jenner (Photo: AKM-GSI-XPOSURE) 
Kendall, who arrived solo save for a burly bodyguard, was soon followed by mum Kris and her sister. 
Braless Kourtney made sure she had all eyes her way dressed in a plunging white bodysuit that was almost see-through. 
While Kris kept things simple in a black top, black trousers and a simple black jacket that featured white stripes. 
It's not the first time this week Kendall has added an injection of colour into her wardrobe. Kendall Jenner (Photo: AZ-ROL/X17online.com) Kendall Jenner (Photo: Splash News) Kendall Jenner (Photo: Splash News) 
Just days ago, the Victoria's Secret beauty was pictured behind the scenes on a bright and beautiful photoshoot in Miami. 
The stunning Kardashian-Jenner offspring looked happy and relaxed as she posed in a sheer bright red lace bra, matching knickers and red heels. 
Laying on her side while surrounded by giant brightly coloured fake flowers and grass, she was showing off her abs and legs in all their glory in the pretty lingerie set. Like us on Facebook
